{"ID":"20240223102610-nkb2vnv","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240223102610-nkb2vnv","title":"材质识别","type":"doc","updated":"20250211104604"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240319100333-2ixr34n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240319100333-2ixr34n"}},{"ID":"20240223102610-pr6v6zw","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240223102610-pr6v6zw","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"电机的一致性问题"}]},{"ID":"20240223103240-5iz9hlk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240223103240-5iz9hlk","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"输出功率"}]},{"ID":"20240223112306-i29qbp4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112306-i29qbp4","updated":"20240223112306"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"输出功率是电机转换电能为机械能的能力，通常以瓦特（W）为单位。输出功率的问题可能包括："}]},{"ID":"20240223112306-x1o7n1w","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112306-x1o7n1w","updated":"20240223112306"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112306-7znnv1n","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112306-7znnv1n","updated":"20240223112306"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112306-ocvnre1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112306-ocvnre1","updated":"20240223112306"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"功率不足"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机无法达到标称功率，导致驱动设备或负载的性能不佳。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112306-go3nmm2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112306-go3nmm2","updated":"20240223112306"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112306-v9qvzb8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112306-v9qvzb8","updated":"20240223112306"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"功率波动"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机在运行过程中输出功率不稳定，可能由电源不稳、电机内部组件磨损或损坏等原因引起。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240223103300-w2xlrbm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240223103300-w2xlrbm","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"效率"}]},{"ID":"20240223112315-mnu8zfd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112315-mnu8zfd","updated":"20240223112315"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"效率是指电机输出功率与输入电功率的比值，表示电机转换能量的效率。电机效率的问题可能包括："}]},{"ID":"20240223112315-pyprf36","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112315-pyprf36","updated":"20240223112315"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112315-1m1126e","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112315-1m1126e","updated":"20240223112315"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112315-3xlwqi0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112315-3xlwqi0","updated":"20240223112315"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"低效率"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机消耗的电能大部分转化为热能而非机械能，导致能源浪费和过热。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112315-kl6l8td","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112315-kl6l8td","updated":"20240223112315"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112315-q9p0pba","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112315-q9p0pba","updated":"20240223112315"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"效率下降"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：随着使用时间的增长，电机的效率可能因磨损、污染、温度升高等因素而下降。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240223103320-nnfzqfy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240223103320-nnfzqfy","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用寿命"}]},{"ID":"20240223112327-7kuqlc5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-7kuqlc5","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"寿命是指电机在性能开始显著下降或完全失效之前可以正常运行的时间。电机寿命的问题可能包括："}]},{"ID":"20240223112327-ga05aoz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-ga05aoz","updated":"20240223112710"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112327-v6udcj4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-v6udcj4","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112327-zqxe0ka","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-zqxe0ka","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"早期失败"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：由于制造缺陷、不当使用或超负荷运行，电机可能在预期寿命之前就发生故障。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112327-8hfx4uo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-8hfx4uo","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112327-q7mg6h4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-q7mg6h4","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"磨损和老化"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机内部的机械部件（如轴承）和电气组件（如绝缘材料）会随着时间和使用而磨损和老化，从而缩短电机寿命。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112327-scccdn2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-scccdn2","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112327-lubrr65","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112327-lubrr65","updated":"20240223112327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"环境因素"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：高温、湿度、灰尘和腐蚀性环境等外部条件也会加速电机的磨损和老化。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112653-a7dz0c1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112653-a7dz0c1","updated":"20240223112710"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112653-govr9ye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112653-govr9ye","updated":"20240223112710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"碳刷"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112111-htjd707","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240223112111-htjd707","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"工艺参数"}]},{"ID":"20240223112124-vpajqau","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240223112124-vpajqau","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"TN曲线"}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-awndzx6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-awndzx6","updated":"20240223112841"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"电机的T-N曲线（也称为转矩-转速曲线）描述了电机在不同转速下的转矩输出能力。"}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-qt5ywr5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-qt5ywr5","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"转矩-转速曲线的关键点包括："}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-hb41l64","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-hb41l64","updated":"20240223112820"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-620br78","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-620br78","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-q0i27p6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-q0i27p6","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"起动转矩（Starting Torque）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机从静止状态开始加速时的初始转矩。对于许多应用来说，一个高的起动转矩是必需的，以克服静止时的摩擦和惯性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-6ty40ks","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-6ty40ks","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-dph2wqu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-dph2wqu","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"最大转矩（Maximum Torque）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机能够产生的最大转矩，通常在转速较低时达到。超过这一点可能会导致电机过热和损坏。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-yljpwyx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-yljpwyx","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-l1609dy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-l1609dy","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"额定转矩（Rated Torque）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机在额定转速和额定功率下可以持续输出的转矩。这是电机长时间安全运行的转矩值。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-9ne16x7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-9ne16x7","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-ugd2zrh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-ugd2zrh","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"无负载转速（No-load Speed）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：电机在没有负载时的最大转速。在这个转速下，电机的输出转矩接近零。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-f8evnwh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-f8evnwh","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-yili1lg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-yili1lg","updated":"20240223112819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"拖动转矩（Pull-out Torque）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：也称为断续转矩，是电机在运行过程中能够短时间内提供的最大转矩，超过这个值可能会导致电机失速。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-qsyazs8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-qsyazs8","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"T"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"−"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"N"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曲线的形状"}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-of6s7t4","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-of6s7t4","updated":"20240223113032"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-03e9hzq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-03e9hzq","updated":"20240223113030"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-iw23626","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-iw23626","updated":"20240223113030"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"直流电机"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"T"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"−"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"N"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曲线通常呈线性下降，起动转矩高，随着转速的增加，转矩逐渐减小。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-6oqlup8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-6oqlup8","updated":"20240223113031"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-zww3zix","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-zww3zix","updated":"20240223113031"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"感应电机"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"T"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"−"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"N"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曲线起始于较高的起动转矩，然后迅速下降至最小值，随后随着转速的增加而逐渐增加至额定转矩，最后在接近同步转速时转矩下降。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240223112819-opyzs0b","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-opyzs0b","updated":"20240223113032"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240223112819-kmqwzb6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240223112819-kmqwzb6","updated":"20240223113032"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"同步电机"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"T"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"−"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"N"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"曲线则表现为在同步转速下转矩突然下降到零，因为同步电机只能在或接近其同步转速下运行。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240227160342-cm35o1z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240227160342-cm35o1z","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"电流