raph","Properties":{"id":"20240529160638-llp5o6f","updated":"20240423141453"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"25.2"}]},{"ID":"20240529160636-daiiovc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240529160636-daiiovc","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"逻辑"}]},{"ID":"20240603164235-hojxyp2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240603164235-hojxyp2","updated":"20240603165127"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"初始开机状态下——\u003e电流保持在0.68A以下保持持续7s，滚刷应该为低转速2200转左右（表示判断正确：地板模式）——\u003e此时加大电流至0.75A以上保持6s以上——\u003e此时滚刷转速应提高至3000转以上（表示判断正确：地毯模式），出现转速变化时需要同步将电流保持在1.2A以上（维持地毯模式）——\u003e1.2A保持5s，如果转速未降低表示地毯模式维持正常——\u003e此时将电流将至0.75A以下保持6s以上——\u003e此时滚刷转速应降低至2200转左右（表示判断正确：地板模式）,出现转速变化时需要同步将电流保持在0.68A以下（维持地板模式）——\u003e0.68A保持5s，如果转速未提高表示地板模式维持正常——\u003e流程判断结束"}]},{"ID":"20240704150418-au2mdyj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704150418-au2mdyj","updated":"20240704150418"}},{"ID":"20240704150425-u54ao9w","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240704150425-u54ao9w","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"转速逻辑"}]},{"ID":"20240704150430-awtu0m6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704150430-awtu0m6","updated":"20240704151135"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"正常运行逻辑：开机默认地板模式，当理论转速值大于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"设定的阈值"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"时，判断为地毯提高转速；当理论转速值小于设定的阈值时，判断为地板降低转速。"}]},{"ID":"20240704150556-gwt8tgr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704150556-gwt8tgr","updated":"20240704150942"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"开机自校验逻辑："}]},{"ID":"20240704151213-z9kkm6n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704151213-z9kkm6n","updated":"20240704151405"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t\t "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"校验触发条件："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.校验电压点（27v~28v \u0026 25v~26v  注意电压点并不是完全和电池包电压一直，在程序中转换时会有一定的）；2.地板模式持续20s以上；3.在此20s内的转速差异不大；4.每次开机均只校验一次；"}]},{"ID":"20240704150944-msjyh3q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704150944-msjyh3q","updated":"20240704151408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t\t "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"校验触发成功："},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将当前收集的转速值和flash中的转速值进行比较，如果转速差异满足变化幅度则记录变化值，并更新"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"color: var(--b3-font-color8);"},"TextMarkType":"text","TextMarkTextContent":"设定的阈值"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"color: var(--b3-font-color8);\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（如：转速比以前的低了就将阈值往下降，反之上升），然后将新的转速值覆盖掉原先的转速值用于下一次比较，"}]},{"ID":"20240704151218-cch6vtz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704151218-cch6vtz","updated":"20240704151218"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\t\t"}]},{"ID":"20240704150933-x0vlure","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240704150933-x0vlure","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"采样频率"}]},{"ID":"20240704151212-9l5cp4d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240704151212-9l5cp4d","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么以前是100us采集一次，现在是416us采集一次？"}]},{"ID":"20240704154933-4ubodao","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240704154933-4ubodao","updated":"20240704160040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240704154936-7jqtz6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704154936-7jqtz6j","updated":"20240704155810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原来的时钟分频是48分频，电机频率为1khz，也就是1s进行1000次周期运动，1s/1khz = 0.001s = 1ms = 1000us, 也就是100us触发一次中断采集， 即1s采集10次"}]},{"ID":"20240704155812-xyeuru4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704155812-xyeuru4","updated":"20240704160040"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现在为了在电机的三角波输出最高点采集电流，并且是2.4khz采集，所以采用20分频，然后 1s/2.4khz = 0.416ms =416us, 也就是416us触发中断采集一次adc，即1s只能采集两次"}]}]},{"ID":"20240704155633-gi3l3xs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704155633-gi3l3xs","updated":"20240704155633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 kHz 意味着每秒钟有 1000 次周期（赫兹表示频率，单位是每秒的周期数）。"}]},{"ID":"20240704155633-4uyzo76","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704155633-4uyzo76","updated":"20240704155633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"计算如下："}]},{"ID":"20240704155633-t86am9s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704155633-t86am9s","updated":"20240704155633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{周期时间} = \\frac{1 \\text{秒}}{1 \\text{kHz}}"}]},{"ID":"20240704155633-j566ebp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704155633-j566ebp","updated":"20240704155633"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于 1 kHz 等于 1000 Hz，因此："}]},{"ID":"20240704155633-mrc49dk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240704155633-mrc49dk","updated":"20240708100652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{周期时间} = \\frac{1 \\text{秒}}{1000} = 0.001 \\text{秒} = 1 \\text{毫秒}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n"}]},{"ID":"20240708092333-t2z0cia","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708092333-t2z0cia","updated":"20240708092333"}},{"ID":"20240708092313-awmszbh","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240708092313-awmszbh","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.4khz的电机怎么配置的"}]},{"ID":"20240708092331-a0jzusk","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240708092331-a0jzusk","updated":"20240731132015"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\n/*************************************************************/\n//ETP0 Functions\n//EntryParameter:NONE\n//ReturnValue:NONE\n/*************************************************************/ \nvoid EPT_CONFIG(void)\n{\n\tEPT_Software_Prg();\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t//EPT software reset\n//------------  EPT GPIO Setting  --------------------------------/\n\t//EPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHAX,IO_NUM_PA00);\t\t\t//AX channel selection\n\t//EPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHAY,IO_NUM_PA01);\t\t\t//AY channel selection\n\t//EPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHBX,IO_NUM_PA07);\t\t\t//BX channel selection\n\tEPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHBY,IO_NUM_PA08);\t\t\t//BY channel selection\n\t//EPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHCX,IO_NUM_PB04);\t\t\t//CX channel selection\n//\tEPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHCY,IO_NUM_PB05);\t\t\t//CY channel selection\n\t//EPT_IO_SET(EPT_IO_CHD,IO_NUM_PA13);\t\t\t//D channel selection\n//------------  EPT Control  --------------------------------/\n\t//计数模式为先上升后下降，且为连续输出\n\tEPT_PWM_Config(EPT_Selecte_PCLK,EPT_CNTMD_increaseTOdecrease,EPT_OPM_Continue,0);//PCLK as clock，increasing mode,continuous mode,TCLK=PCLK/(0+1) EPT_CNTMD_increase\n\t//EPT_Tevent_Selecte(0x00,0x00);\t\t\t\t//T1 source selection SYNCIN4,T2 source selectionSYNCIN5\n\t//EPT_SYNCR_Config(EPT_Triggle_Continue,EPT_SYNCUSR0_REARMTrig_DIS,EPT_TRGSRC0_ExtSync_SYNCUSR0,EPT_TRGSRC1_ExtSync_SYNCUSR4,0x30);//enable SYNCUSR4 SYNCUSR5 as trigger event,continuous mode\n\t//EPT_PWMX_Output_Control(EPT_PWMA,EPT_CA_Selecte_CMPA,EPT_CB_Selecte_CMPA,EPT_PWM_ZRO_Event_OutHigh,EPT_PWM_PRD_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_CAU_Event_OutLow,EPT_PWM_CAD_Event_OutLow,\n\t//\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CBU_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_CBD_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T1U_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T1D_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T2U_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T2D_Event_Nochange);\n\tEPT_PWMX_Output_Control(EPT_PWMB,//选择 EPT_PWMB 通道。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_CA_Selecte_CMPB,//比较寄存器 A 和 B 都选择 CMPB。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_CB_Selecte_CMPB,。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_ZRO_Event_OutLow,//在计数器为零时，输出低电平。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_PRD_Event_Nochange,//在计数器达到周期值时，不改变输出。 \n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CAU_Event_OutHigh,//在计数器向上计数且达到比较寄存器 A 值时，输出高电平。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CAD_Event_OutLow,//在计数器向下计数且达到比较寄存器 A 值时，输出低电平。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CBU_Event_Nochange,//在计数器向上计数且达到比较寄存器 B 值时，不改变输出。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CBD_Event_Nochange,//在计数器向下计数且达到比较寄存器 B 值时，不改变输出。\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_T1U_Event_Nochange, //计数器 T1 和 T2 在向上和向下计数时都不改变输出。\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_T1D_Event_Nochange,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_T2U_Event_Nochange,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_T2D_Event_Nochange);\n\t\t\n\t//EPT_PWMX_Output_Control(EPT_PWMC,EPT_CA_Selecte_CMPC,EPT_CB_Selecte_CMPC,EPT_PWM_ZRO_Event_OutHigh,EPT_PWM_PRD_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_CAU_Event_OutLow,EPT_PWM_CAD_Event_OutLow,\n\t//\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CBU_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_CBD_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T1U_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T1D_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T2U_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T2D_Event_Nochange);\n\t//EPT_PWMX_Output_Control(EPT_PWMD,EPT_CA_Selecte_CMPD,EPT_CB_Selecte_CMPD,EPT_PWM_ZRO_Event_OutHigh,EPT_PWM_PRD_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_CAU_Event_OutLow,EPT_PWM_CAD_Event_OutLow,\n\t//\t\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PWM_CBU_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_CBD_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T1U_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T1D_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T2U_Event_Nochange,EPT_PWM_T2D_Event_Nochange);\n//\tEPT_PRDR_CMPA_CMPB_CMPC_CMPD_Config(20000,0,20000,0,0);//PRDR=2400,CMPA=1200,CMPB=600,CMPC=2400,CMPD=0\n\tEPT_PRDR_CMPA_CMPB_CMPC_CMPD_Config(10000,0,0,0,0);\n\tEPT_DB_CLK_Config(0,24,24);//Fdbclk=Fhclk/(0+1)，DTR=24clk，DTF=24clk 这个是死区时钟频率配置\n\t//EPT_DBCR_Config(EPT_CHA_Selecte,EPT_CHAINSEL_PWMA_RISE_FALL,EPT_CHA_OUTSEL_EnRise_EnFall,EPT_PB_OUT_Reverse,EPT_PAtoCHX_PBtoCHY);//PWMA Complementary,CHX rising edge,CHY falling edge\n\tEPT_DBCR_Config(EPT_CHB_Selecte,\n\t\t\t\t\tEPT_CHBINSEL_PWMB_RISE_FALL,\n\t\t\t\t\tEPT_CHB_OUTSEL_EnRise_EnFall,\n\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PB_OUT_Reverse,\n\t\t\t\t\tEPT_PAtoCHX_PBtoCHY);//PWMB Complementary,CHX rising edge,CHY falling edge\n\t\n\t//EPT_DBCR_Config(EPT_CHC_Selecte,EPT_CHCINSEL_PWMC_RISE_FALL,EPT_CHC_OUTSEL_EnRise_EnFall,EPT_PB_OUT_Reverse,EPT_PAtoCHX_PBtoCHY);//PWMC Complementary,CHX rising edge,CHY falling edge\n//------------  EPT interruption  --------------------------------/\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAP_LD0);//CMPA load interrupt\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAP_LD1);//CMPB load interrupt\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAP_LD2);//CMPC load interrupt\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAP_LD3);//CMPD load interrupt\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAU);//Up-Counting phase CNT = CMPA interrupt request raw status\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAD);//Down-Counting phase CNT = CMPA interrupt request raw statu\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CBU);//Up-Counting phase CNT = CMPB interrupt request raw status\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CBD);//Down-Counting phase CNT = CMPB interrupt request raw status\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CCU);//Up-Counting phase CNT = CMPC interrupt request raw status\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CCD);//Down-Counting phase CNT = CMPC interrupt request raw status\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CDU);//Up-Counting phase CNT = CMPD interrupt request raw status\n\t//EPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CDD);//Down-Counting phase CNT = CMPD interrupt request raw status\n\tEPT_Int_Enable(EPT_PEND);//触发中断\n\tEPT_Vector_Int_Enable();\n//------------  EPT start  --------------------------------/\n\n//------------  EPT capture config  --------------------------------/\n\t/*EPT_Software_Prg();\n\tEPT_Capture_Config(EPT_Selecte_PCLK,EPT_CNTMD_increase,EPT_CAPMD_Continue,EPT_CAP_EN,EPT_LDARST_EN,EPT_LDBRST_DIS,EPT_LDCRST_DIS,EPT_LDDRST_DIS,1,0);//TCLK=pclk/(1+0),CMPAload CMPBload\n\tEPT_SYNCR_Config(EPT_Triggle_Continue,EPT_SYNCUSR0_REARMTrig_DIS,EPT_TRGSRC0_ExtSync_SYNCUSR0,EPT_TRGSRC1_ExtSync_SYNCUSR4,0x04);//Enable SYNCUSR2 ,Continuous trigger\n\tEPT_PRDR_CMPA_CMPB_CMPC_CMPD_Config(0XFFFF,0,0,0,0);\n\tEPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAP_LD0);//Capture Load to CMPA interrupt request raw status\n\tEPT_Int_Enable(EPT_CAP_LD1);//Capture Load to CMPB interrupt request raw status\n\tEPT_Vector_Int_Enable();\n\tEPT_Start();*/\n}\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-20gecfk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-20gecfk","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.4khz的配置"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-g4yssfy","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-g4yssfy","updated":"20240708104146"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240708093559-8u2zxa0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-8u2zxa0","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.首先时钟频率是48MHz，周期寄存器的配置为10000次，即EPT_PRDR_CMPA_CMPB_CMPC_CMPD_Config(10000,0,0,0,0); PRDR=10000\n2."}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-ufqgdel","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-ufqgdel","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"周期时间 = 周期寄存器的配置 / 时钟频率 =（10000+1）/ 48000000≈208.35微秒"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-6rbfy73","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-6rbfy73","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对应的频率为："}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-0j3qie8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-0j3qie8","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{频率} = \\frac{1}{\\text{周期时间}}"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-u41yf19","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-u41yf19","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{频率} \\approx \\frac{1}{208.35 \\times 10^{-6}} \\approx 4.8 \\text{kHz}"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-sj7gjrq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-sj7gjrq","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.EPT_PWM_Config(EPT_Selecte_PCLK, EPT_CNTMD_increaseTOdecrease, EPT_OPM_Continue, 0);"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-t3r8lxi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-t3r8lxi","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"又因为配置的计数方式是上升-下降模式，这种模式下计数器将从0计数到10000，再从10000计数到0，所以一个完整的周期包含两个计数周期"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-whq80eo","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-whq80eo","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708093559-xl65zqx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-xl65zqx","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708093559-mgzsrha","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-mgzsrha","updated":"20240708093559"}}]}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-3tkyszc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-3tkyszc","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总周期时间=2×208.35微秒≈416.7微秒"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-d2gcbxh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-d2gcbxh","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对应的频率为："}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-vz2cae3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-vz2cae3","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{频率} = \\frac{1}{\\text{总周期时间}}"}]},{"ID":"20240708093559-pz7ru21","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093559-pz7ru21","updated":"20240708093559"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{频率} \\approx \\frac{1}{416.7 \\times 10^{-6}} \\approx 2.4 \\text{kHz}"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708104146-2plm0v2","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":5,"Properties":{"id":"20240708104146-2plm0v2","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"绿灯配置"}]},{"ID":"20240708095347-rk7am90","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240708095347-rk7am90","updated":"20240708104154"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240708095350-ksahu2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708095350-ksahu2a","updated":"20240708095452"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"像之前绿灯的配置是"}]},{"ID":"20240708101812-3pmqggw","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240708101812-3pmqggw","updated":"20240708103603"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"EPT_PWMX_Output_Control(EPT_PWMC,\n\nEPT_CA_Selecte_CMPC,\n\nEPT_CB_Selecte_CMPC,\n\nEPT_PWM_ZRO_Event_OutHigh,//计数到0时输出高电平\n\nEPT_PWM_PRD_Event_Nochange,\n\nEPT_PWM_CAU_Event_OutLow,//在计数器向上计数且达到比较寄存器 A 值时，输出低电平。\n\nEPT_PWM_CAD_Event_OutLow,\nEPT_PWM_CBU_Event_Nochange,\n\nEPT_PWM_CBD_Event_Nochange,\n\nEPT_PWM_T1U_Event_Nochange,\n\nEPT_PWM_T1D_Event_Nochange,\n\nEPT_PWM_T2U_Event_Nochange,\n\nEPT_PWM_T2D_Event_Nochange);\n\n#define    duty_cycle_40() \tEPT_PRDR_CMPA_CMPB_CMPC_CMPD_Config(40000,0,0,24000,0);\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240708101820-bz6yyxf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708101820-bz6yyxf","updated":"20240708101822"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表示："}]},{"ID":"20240708095452-c5da3ou","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708095452-c5da3ou","updated":"20240708095458"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"计数周期是40000"}]},{"ID":"20240708095459-10ccu2x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708095459-10ccu2x","updated":"20240708103732"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"24000/40000 = 0.6\n即占空比输出应该为60%\n但又因为配置中设置了计数到周期计数值时输出低电平，所以60%输出为低电平，所以结果就是40%高电平"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708093600-t5ufiku","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240708093600-t5ufiku","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"占空比设置"}]},{"ID":"20240708093628-19mx1po","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240708093628-19mx1po","updated":"20240708093857"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\n\nvoid Set_Duty(uint32_t duty)\n{ \n\t//duty =1000;\n\t//duty =(10000 - duty) / 2;\n\t//duty =duty / 2;\n\tEPT_PRDR_CMPA_CMPB_CMPC_CMPD_Config(10000,0,duty,0,0); //duty = 16000\n}\n\nvoid Brush_Duty_Set(uint32_t x)\n{\n\n\tif(x\u003e=1000)\n\t{\n\t\tx = 1000; \n\t}\n\tx = x * 10;\n\n\tSet_Duty(x);\n\n\t//BT_Period_CMP_Write(BT0,1000,x);\n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240708093654-x31npw3","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240708093654-x31npw3","updated":"20240708120316"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240708093655-qyul4ps","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093655-qyul4ps","updated":"20240708093725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.其中 10000表示周期寄存器的计数周期值为10000次"}]},{"ID":"20240708093725-9xkf0fz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093725-9xkf0fz","updated":"20240708093754"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.又因为电机用的是通道B，所以第三位设置的 duty"}]},{"ID":"20240708093754-blxhrtx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093754-blxhrtx","updated":"20240708093819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.占空比=EPT_PRDR_Value / EPT_CMPB_Value × 100%"}]},{"ID":"20240708093820-t6qaijv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093820-t6qaijv","updated":"20240708093821"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4."}]},{"ID":"20240708093926-a2ity7g","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-a2ity7g","updated":"20240708093926"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708093926-xj1z4gk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-xj1z4gk","updated":"20240708093926"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708093926-d9d6j5t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-d9d6j5t","updated":"20240708093926"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"EPT_CMPB_Value"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 是比较寄存器 B 的值，控制 PWM 的高电平持续时间。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708093926-kxfev94","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-kxfev94","updated":"20240708093926"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708093926-ur3zqeh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-ur3zqeh","updated":"20240708093926"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"EPT_PRDR_Value"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 是计时器的周期值，控制 PWM 的周期。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240708093926-sug9ow7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-sug9ow7","updated":"20240708093926"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"例如，如果 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"duty"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 设置为 5000，那么 PWM 的占空比为："}]},{"ID":"20240708093926-nld26f3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708093926-nld26f3","updated":"20240708094141"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\text{占空比} = \\frac{5000}{10000} \\times 100\\% = 50\\%"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n5.我们现在写的是0-1000是因为我们原来的占空比分辨率设置的0-1000，然后现在计数周期改为10000了，所以按照现在的2.4khz配置方式需要将占空比扩大10倍"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708120316-a95f47v","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240708120316-a95f47v","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中断触发采集adc"}]},{"ID":"20240708120338-8s3p6nd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708120338-8s3p6nd","updated":"20240731132050"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 33%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240708120338-ftwqz7z.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 33%;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 75%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240708155610-q04pnuj.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 75%;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeBr","Data":"br"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 50%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240708141433-qjlohwi.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 50%;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"parent-style":"width: 50%;","style":"width: 10000px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240708120438-6g3jz49.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 10000px;\" parent-style=\"width: 50%;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240708155610-cbt8b8i","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240708155610-cbt8b8i","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240731133526-jlt308t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240731133526-jlt308t","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"通常情况下，电流的波动在特定时间内会达到最大值。电机的电流特性通常是周期性的，尤其是在对称模式下，电流会在正弦波或其他周期性波形的情况下波动。"}]},{"ID":"20240731133526-bugm3vf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240731133526-bugm3vf","updated":"20240731133526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你在对称模式下进行PWM控制时，电机的电流会在周期内变化，这些变化通常会在周期的某些时刻达到最大值。 如果你的计数器用于检测PWM信号的周期，并且在周期的某个特定点（例如计数溢出点）触发ADC采集，那么在对称模式下，这个采集点很可能会接近或正好是电流的最大值。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708120325-93fcbm5","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240708120325-93fcbm5","updated":"20240708141527"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240708120326-zi1cc4v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708120326-zi1cc4v","updated":"20240708141527"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当ept触发中断的时候就会进行adc采集，EPTIntHandler中断即电机pwm驱动会先使能adc中断，然后ADCIntHandler会进行采集"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708093944-72xhy8e","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240708093944-72xhy8e","updated":"20241119133504"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死区时钟频率配置"}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-hu6nrgq","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-hu6nrgq","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708100602-16cgpzl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-16cgpzl","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708100602-hozes6n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-hozes6n","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"死区时钟频率"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":":"}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-2l51dzy","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-2l51dzy","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yw=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"EPT_DB_CLK_Config(0, 24, 24);\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-x7wo2e7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-x7wo2e7","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据函数的定义，死区时钟频率的计算公式为："}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-rjek63e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-rjek63e","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_{dbclk} = \\frac{F_{hclk}}{DPSC + 1}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其中，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"F_{hclk}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 是系统时钟频率（48 MHz），"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DPSC"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 是死区时钟分频器值（0）。"}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-51n3rtu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-51n3rtu","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此："}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-okkvo8v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-okkvo8v","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"F_{dbclk} = \\frac{48 \\text{ MHz}}{0 + 1} = 48 \\text{ MHz}"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-77ywccr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-77ywccr","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708100602-uxmr5uf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-uxmr5uf","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"死区上升时间和下降时间"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":":"}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-bef7dm7","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-bef7dm7","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708100602-66zr7lv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-66zr7lv","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708100602-y9ud7ru","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-y9ud7ru","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DTR = 24"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-0r4narh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-0r4narh","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240708100602-51aswee","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-51aswee","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DTF = 24"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-dzgp0in","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-dzgp0in","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"死区时间（上升和下降时间）以死区时钟周期为单位，因此上升和下降时间分别为：\n"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"T_{rise} = T_{fall} = \\frac{DTR}{F_{dbclk}} = \\frac{DTF}{F_{dbclk}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"带入数值："}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-752fezu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-752fezu","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"T_{rise} = T_{fall} = \\frac{24}{48 \\text{ MHz}} = 0.5 \\text{ μs}"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240708100602-v1dvyog","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240708100602-v1dvyog","updated":"20240708100602"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，在48 MHz时钟频率下，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DPSC"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 为0，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DTR"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"DTF"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 为24的配置下，死区上升和下降时间分别为0.5微秒"}]},{"ID":"20240708120312-cj9561f","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240708120312-cj9561f","updated":"20241119133713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"超声波材质识别"}]},{"ID":"20241119133506-dfgzbg3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20241119133506-dfgzbg3","updated":"20241119133713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"超声波受脏污影响"}]},{"ID":"20241119133628-yn87mc6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241119133628-yn87mc6","updated":"20241119133713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不受影响"}]},{"ID":"20241119133700-i0ovtvz","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20241119133700-i0ovtvz","updated":"20241119133713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20241119133700-kxg51es","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241119133700-kxg51es","updated":"20241119133713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不受影响，地板地毯识别准确"}]}]},{"ID":"20241119133536-36kp5jh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241119133536-36kp5jh","updated":"20241119133638"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"height: 50vh;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"rename_file"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/rename_file-20241119133536-tuj1ssw.jpeg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"height: 50vh;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"height: 50vh;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"rename_file"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/rename_file-20241119133558-ml4bcl8.jpeg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"height: 50vh;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20241119133623-tmo5uei","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20241119133623-tmo5uei","updated